name: Moon Elite
description:
This is Moon Elite Logo #1 out of 228 Items (Countries + Our Logo) on the moon. Created by Global Moon Club ( MoonElite.com ), Multi Token Standard on the Polygon Blockchain for the people who proud and love of their country and enjoy traveling to other countries.
Own 1 or 3 of the 228 items available to get the Following Features :
1- Add Beauty and Patriotism to your Collection Wallet, by Get item of your Country's Flag on the Moon.
2- Build Together the Largest Community in the world.
3-After you own our Token item, you Become a Participant with us in Saving People's Lives (children - women - elderly), providing food, water and treatment (operations, medicines, care) for them, through Donations that will be in the Phase 4 Mentioned by our ROADMAP. (Don't forget: Doing good and saving people's lives, all of this opens the doors to success and happiness in your life).
4- If you are Lucky, you will Win one of our Valuable Gifts Mentioned in our ROADMAP.
5- Get Authorization to enter our Future Game (Play & Earn) on WEB 3 (Metaverse, etc.).
 Original Size is 3001 x 3000.
